<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.6.1">
<l>akkum puliyiṉ ataḷu muṭaiyā ravaroruvar</l>
<l>pakkam niṟka niṉṟa paṇpa rūrpōlum</l>
<l>takka marattiṉ tāḻci ṉaiyēṟi tāyvāyil</l>
<l>kokkiṉ piḷḷai veḷḷi ṟavuṇṇuṅ kuṟuṅkuṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kuṟuṅkuṭi, where climbing on a convenient lower branch of a tree,</l>
<l>A heron chick eats white shrimp from the mother’s mouth,</l>
<l>Is like the city of the one of quality who stands [there]</l>
<l>While the one who has bone [beads] and a tiger skin stands at [his] side.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
